      "startTime": 172.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "こんばんはー！　TRINITYAiLEの\n鈴村優です！　今日は、うちらのライブにようこそ！",
      "startTime": 176.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 466.6666666999788,
          "startTime": 174.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "先日はうち、風邪でイベント休んで\n心配掛けてしまってごめんなさい",
      "startTime": 185.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "でも、完全復活です！\nむしろ休養になって、以前より元気なくらいです",
      "startTime": 191.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu026.m4a",
      "text": "うちな、今回周囲の人に……ファンのみなさんや\nスタッフさんにいっぱい心配してもらって",
      "startTime": 201.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu027.m4a",
      "text": "助けてもらってるんやなって、みんなのおかげで\nステージに立ててるんやなって実感しました",
      "startTime": 207.7409199289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu028.m4a",
      "text": "うちは幸せ者です\n今夜は目一杯楽しんでいって下さい！",
      "startTime": 214.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu029.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、一曲目いきましょか～",
      "startTime": 218.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2466.666666700007,
          "startTime": 220.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（……いいステージだ。ありがとう、鈴村さん）\n（最高の恩返しだよ）",
      "startTime": 227.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu030.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます～",
      "startTime": 229.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_03-yu031.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみなさん！　スタッフのみなさん！\nそれから――",
      "startTime": 235.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
